de.upb.m2m.quality.casestudies.javaemf
Class UML2RDBMS

java.lang.Object
  de.upb.m2m.quality.casestudies.javaemf.UML2RDBMS

public class UML2RDBMS
extends java.lang.Object

This class implements the transformation from a SimpleUML to a SimpleRDBMS model via Java plus EMF technology. The main method executes the transformation.

Version:
0.1
Author:
Sebastian Lehrig (lehrig@mail.upb.de)
